<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186783>
    bibo:endPage "22" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "2059" ;
    dc:creator "Bauer, Christian; Prieto, Carlos E." ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Three new Assamiidae (Arachnida: Opiliones) from Cameroon, with a redescription of Chilon robustus and comments on related species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186784>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186785>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186789>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186792> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186784>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Dorsal (left) and ventral (right) views of males. 1 – 2, Chilon robustus Sørensen, 1896. 3 – 4, Ereca treses sp. nov. 5 – 6, Bueana vitteli sp. nov. 7 – 8. Rhabdopygus puylaerti sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186784/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186785>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 14. External morphology of Chilon robustus Sørensen, 1896 (male from Buea, MRAC / 135327). 9, body, dorsal view. 10, body, ventral view. 11, body, lateral view. 12, body, posterior view. 13, right chelicera, ectal view. 14, right pedipalp, mesal view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186785/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186789>
    dc:description "FIGURES 36 – 47. Chilon spp., penis head in ventral (36, 40, 44), lateral (37, 41, 45) and dorsal view (38, 42, 46), and total penis in dorsal view (39, 43, 47). 36 – 39, Chilon robustus Sørensen, 1896 (Buea, MRAC / 135327). 40 – 43. Chilon robustus Sørensen, 1896 (syntype, Kamerum, NHRS). 44 – 47. Chilon undulatus Sørensen, 1896 (syntype, Kamerum, NHRS). Scale bars: Left 0.1 mm, right 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186789/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186792>
    dc:description "FIGURES 68 – 70. Ovipositors (with detail of their hair tips). 68. Chilon robustus Sørensen, 1896. 69. Ereca treses sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

